# Binomio de Newton

$$(a+b)^n = \sum_{k=0}^n {n\choose k} \cdot a^{n-k} \cdot b^k = {n\choose 0}*a^n*b^0 + \cdots {n\choose n}*a^0*b^n $$

# Funci칩n con R

```{r}
binomioNewton = function(a,b,n){
  cumsum(choose(n,(0:n))*a^{n-(0:n)}*b^(0:n))[n+1]
}
binomioNewton(2,1,2)
binomioNewton(3,4,14)
```

